    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the demo version of All On Board!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try this immersive VR platform and enjoy digital versions of the tabletop games you love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo, you can play for up to two hours for free, with access to all free classic games and all available DLCs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251900/extras/60bad8480ed8bf049ce91ace5e01a0c7.poster.avif?t=1768302376\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251900/extras/60bad8480ed8bf049ce91ace5e01a0c7.webm?t=1768302376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251900/extras/60bad8480ed8bf049ce91ace5e01a0c7.mp4?t=1768302376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The laughter, the rivalry, the quiet focus before a decisive roll, it’s all here in VR. Gather around a virtual table that feels real, no matter how far apart you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What you can experience in the demo:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Lifelike VR tabletop experience with realistic physics and intuitive controls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Access to free classic games and preview all available DLCs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Cross-platform multiplayer and multi-language support</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Solo, co-op, or competitive play</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Learning Hub in every game to help you learn the rules quickly</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251900/extras/c01a65c48073536706279546dfb52dc6.poster.avif?t=1768302376\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251900/extras/c01a65c48073536706279546dfb52dc6.webm?t=1768302376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251900/extras/c01a65c48073536706279546dfb52dc6.mp4?t=1768302376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All On Board! features a growing library of free classic games and officially licensed tabletop titles sold separately as DLC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This demo is the perfect way to explore every available DLC in a time-limited preview, experience how each game feels in VR, and decide which ones you want to play next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the demo ends, you can purchase any DLC you like in the full version of All On Board!. Only the host needs to own the selected DLC to start a game, while other players can join with just the base app.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251900/extras/d6cd6664c41d8c93b1d6df0d757d9879.poster.avif?t=1768302376\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251900/extras/d6cd6664c41d8c93b1d6df0d757d9879.webm?t=1768302376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251900/extras/d6cd6664c41d8c93b1d6df0d757d9879.mp4?t=1768302376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All On Board! is made by an independent studio that loves board games as much as you do. It’s built on passion, constant updates, and a growing lineup of great titles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring game nights back to life with All On Board!</p>",
